{"tid":729159,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"求港股投資書","createTime":"2018-07-04T10:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T12:47:42.000Z","uid":109415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"13a09ebc5ae6c6f67bc9d222f19af613ccb4f871","tid":729159,"uid":109415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:12:00.000Z","msg":"見好多書都係講美股<br />\n有無啲書係可以應用到係港股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3d53d9084eb51465a9d29a76beec841ff555d6","tid":729159,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:13:17.000Z","msg":"渾水嗰本唔錯🤔"},{"pid":"742d9006216dbda068e1d17b2a9e1f88f8a406c6","tid":729159,"uid":17765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:14:22.000Z","msg":"因為港股不具投資價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca186c1a8de07eccd58049ad3586ae316a12b50","tid":729159,"uid":17765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:15:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">冇港股書係</span>因為港股不具投資價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0a50c2cc2a6c34fee1b89af02d80b369e68374f2","tid":729159,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/191816_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F191816_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=409b4a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本 IT 狗絕技<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 學炒股前，先學揼 code<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 應該當買港股係買垃圾，當買美股係買金條<br />\n<br />\n3. 垃圾有個賤價，金條亦有個合理價，要搵個價出嚟就需熟悉各行各業嘅估值模型<br />\n<br />\n4. 識計價只係成功嘅一半，另一半就要睇大市 trend。<br />\n<br />\n5. 每個市場、每個行業、每隻股票都有唔同波幅率，最好記熟佢<br />\n<br />\n6. 垃圾港股股災跌你七八成，強勢美股股災只會跌你三四成<br />\n<br />\n7. 市走 down trend 係準備未來掃垃圾嘅時候，但垃圾只可以被「利用」，當垃圾去返正常價嘅時候，應該冇乜利用價值<br />\n<br />\n8. 勿沾牛熊，小注期權<br />\n<br />\n9. 市差沽弱股，市強做強股<br />\n<br />\n10. 經濟數據好撚重要 (eg. PMI、匯率、非農 etc.)"},{"pid":"d713cc4b5bbacc382d3a2d48f75adb3e1169cbd0","tid":729159,"uid":173159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"一步步致富"},{"pid":"b5155c6b6c97b5a70f36785cedc527a465120bab","tid":729159,"uid":26038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:47:42.000Z","msg":"個個投資都求勝 你求輸？"}]}